inn1.comm: short delivery defended to the on side.
up on his toes and defends on the track.
lovely delivery pitches and moves away, beats the outside edge as he plays forward.
good length delivery defended well to the off side.
beauty, pitches it short of a length and moving away, beats the outside edge for the second time in the over.
short ball pulled well in front of square leg to the fence, quickly got into the position.
wide outside the off stump, left alone.
short of a length outside the off stump, up on his toes and drops it square of the wicket on the off side and takes off for a quick single, gets off the mark.
short of a length and coming in, Sibanda moves forward in line and lets it go.
strays down the leg side, signaled wide.
short of a length and in the corridor outside the off stump, covers the line and shoulders arms, through to Ramdin.
drops it square of the wicket on the off side and takes off for another quick single.
another quick single, as Taylor drops it to the on side.
short of a length outside the off stump, Taylor defends to the off side.
left alone outside the off stump.
defends to point.
good length delivery outside the off stump, swings in the air and also moves of the wicket, beats the outside edge as Taylor plays forward.
waits for the delivery and at the last moment opens the face off the bat and runs it down to thirdman, comes quickly back for a tight second run.
yorker outside the off stump, beats the outside edge.
short outside the off stump, watches it well and lets it go through to Ramdin.
short of a length outside the off stump, plays and gets beaten, ball seaming away.
appeal for lbw turned down, pitches outside the off stump and strikes the pad outside the line.
pushes to extra-cover for a quick single.
moves back and pushes in the gap between backward-point and cover for a single.
looking to work it through the on side, misses it, off the pad the ball goes to the off side, they scamper through for a leg-bye.
enough movement to beat the outside edge. Good length delivery outside the off stump, Sibanda plays forward and gets beaten.
short ball pulled in the air to midwicket fence, picked it up well.
beats the outside edge as Sibanda plays forward.
yorker length delivery swinging away, beats the bat and through to Ramdin.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, pitches and moves away beats the outside edge.
fuller delivery on the middle and leg, Sibanda cannot get it away, pushes to the on side.
good length delivery outside the off stump, moves forward in line and shoulders arms.
bit wide outside the off stump, Taylor moves forward and lets it go through to Ramdin.
quick single taken, drops it beside the track on the on side.
short of a length outside the off stump and coming in, left alone.
moves forward and defends to cover.
good length delivery outside the off stump and coming, Sibanda defends on the front foot to the off side.
the ball held up a fraction as Taylor plays forward, goes in the air and falls safely on the off side.
slashes hard in the air over point to the fence. It was wide outside the off stump and Taylor had all the width to put it away.
pushes to cover for another quick single. Good running.
bad line, strays into the pads, Sibanda puts it away to long leg fence.
short outside the off stump, pitches and moves away, plays and misses.
Powell gets the first break-through, pitches outside the off stump on a good length and moves away, Sibanda plays forward and gets an outside edge to Ramdin behind the wicket.
short outside the off stump, Taylor waited for it and drives on the front foot past point to the fence.
drops it square of the wicket on the off side and takes for another single.
plays from the crease to the on side.
short outside the off stump and width offered, Chibhabha cannot put it away, played straight to the fielder at backward point.
driven well this time by Chibhabha, hit on the up in the gap between extra-cover and mid off, the ball races along the turf to the fence.
short outside the off stump, puts it away in style, cuts on the front foot in front of point to the fence.
good areas from Powell outside the off stump, swing and movement off the wicket, left alone.
width offered outside the off stump, cut very hard to the fielder at backward-point.
yorker length outside the off stump, dug out to the off side.
good length delivery coming in, Chibhabha drops it to the off side.
short of a length outside the off stump, left alone.
good length delivery and coming in, plays on the front foot down the track.
good ball coming in, cramps Chibhabha for any room, drops it to the on side.
short and down the leg side, terrible line from Rampaul, signaled wide.
cuts Chibhabha in half as the ball pitches short of a length outside the off stump and comes in.
short of length and on the middle and leg, looks to work it to the on side, misses it, off the body the ball drops on the track.
goes for the big cut on the off side, chops it down hard into the ground.
good ball coming in, defended on the track.
drifts onto middle and leg, off the pad to short fine leg.
beauty from Taylor, pitches outside the off stump and seams away and beats the outside edge.
defended on the front foot to the off side.
strays slightly on the leg side, Chibhabha picks it up nicely and hit in the air to square leg fence, good shot.
off the pad to the on side.
fantastic shot, puts his left foot forward and drives through the off side past the cover fielder to the fence.
pitches it full outside the off stump, driven straight along the ground to the fielder at backward point, the throw is at the non-strikers end, nobody backing up, they get three overthrows.
good ball coming in, drops it on the track
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, gets behind it and forces it to the off side.
good ball back of a length, mistimes it as he forces to the off side.
short ball, Chibhabha rocks on the back foot and pulls in the air over square leg to the fence.

RUN OUT! Pushes to mid-off and takes off for a quick single, Chanderpaul quickly in picks up the ball and strikes the stumps at the non-strikers end, Taylor makes a desperate dive, but he is a long way off.
down the leg side, plays and misses, signaled wide.
defended on the on side.
pulls from outside in front of square leg for couple of runs.
defends with an open face off the bat to backward-point.
good ball back of a length, pitches and moves away, Chibhabha defends to the off side.
moves forward and lets it go outside the off stump.
gets behind the short of a length delivery outside the off stump and defends to the off side.
good ball and well left. Pitches short of a length and seaming in, lets it go through to Ramdin.
good length delivery defended on the front foot to the off side.
short delivery outside the off stump, up on his toes and defends to the on side.
left alone outside the off stump.
moves forward in line and pushes to the on side.
pitched up delivery outside the off stump, Chibhabha drives it along the ground straight to the fielder at extra-cover.
good ball seaming in, Chibhabha defends to the off side.
up on his toes and defends to the off side.
driven to the left of mid-off for a single.
drops it beside the track on the on side and takes off for a quick single, shy at the stumps misses and nobody backing up, they get an overthrow.
driven on the front foot to mid-off.
pushes to the on side for a single.
left alone outside the off stump, good ball in the corridor.
pushes to point and takes off, sent back by Chibhabha.
moves forward and pushes to cover.
defends from the crease to the off side.
lovely shot, goes all the way. Short outside the off stump and Taibu rocks on the back foot and pulls well in the air over the midwicket fence for maximum.
chips it in the air over the bowler, was looking to hit over the in-field.
moves forward and pushes to cover.
moves across his stumps and plays down the track. Taylor does well cramping Taibu for any room.
walks across his stumps and lets it go outside the off stump.
short ball on middle and leg, pulls in the air to fine leg, on the bounce to the fielder.
width offered outside the off stump, Chibhabha need no invitation as he slashes it  in the air over point, reaches the fence in quick time.
moves back and steers it down to thirdman
quick single taken as Chibhabha gets an inside edge to the on side, Bravo follows-through and kicks the ball at the stumps, misses it.
defended to the off side to point.
Bravo strikes, a soft dismissal, good length delivery bit wide outside the off stump, Taibu plays forward and gets an outside edge through to Ramdin, who completes a comfortable catch.
another good delivery in the corridor outside the off stump, moves forward in line and lets it go.
gets behind it and defends to the off side.
pushes forward and drives to cover along the ground to cover.
good length delivery on the off stump, defended to the off side.
mistimes the drive to mid-on.
good intent but no luck as it was driven straight to the fielder along the ground to cover.
tight line from Taylor, Chibhabha is forced to defend to the off side.
short ball slashed away in the air to the left of backward-point, the ball goes along the turf, the thirdman puts in a dive but cannot prevent the ball reaching the fence.
pushes it back down the track.
good length delivery bit wide outside the off stump, moves forward and lets it go through to Ramdin.
moves forward, inside edges onto the pads and the ball rolls to the off side.
looks to drive on up, gets a thickish inside edge and goes along the ground to square leg, too much bottom hand from Masakadza.
moves forward and defends to point and a quick call of no.
slower delivery from Bravo, pushes to mid-on.
good length delivery defended to mid-on.
smashed away on the front foot along the ground straight to the fielder at extra-cover.

short of a length outside the off stump, opens the face off the bat and plays to the left of backward point, Powell running in from thirdman fields the ball, was unhappy with the signaling from his teammates.
good ball, gets an outside edge to thirdman fence.
bad line, drifts down the leg side, signaled wide.
good length delivery defended to the on side.
lovely shot, puts his left foot forward and drives well in the gap between extra-cover and mid-off, the ball travels along the turf to the fence.
beats the outside edge as Masakadza pushes forward.
a thick inside edge onto the pads and then to the off side as Masakadza looks to work it through the on side.
opens the face of the bat and runs it down to thirdman.
fuller length delivery angled in, drifting down the leg side, strikes the pad, loud shout, turned down by umpire Barbour.
bat and pad to the off side.
cut away to the left of backward point to the deep, Samuels fields the ball.
tossed up outside the leg stump, eases it down the ground to long on.
a touch short outside the off stump, pushes to deep point.
waits for the spin and plays past the slip to thirdman.
defended down the track.
eased down the ground to long on.
tosses up on the off and middle, comes forward and defends to the off side.

bit of mix-up as Masakadza drops it square of the wicket on the off side and takes off for a run, yes, no and yes, they run, the throw at the non-strikers end misses, that would have been curtains for Masakadza.
left alone outside the off stump.
opens the face of the bat and glides it down to the left of thirdman, good fielding by Samuels to save couple of runs.
again looks to glide it down to thirdman, beats the outside edge.
dabs it square of the wicket on the off side and looks for a single but a quick call of no.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump, looking to glide it down, beats the outside edge and through to Ramdin.
driven down the ground to long on.
gets to the pitch of the delivery and drives well down the ground to long off.
pushes to the right of backward point and takes off for a quick single.
moves forward and defends to the off side.
down the track and pushes to the left of extra-cover to the deep, looking for the second run, sent back.
waits for the turn and pushes to cover for another single.
short of a length delivery outside the off stump and coming in, defends down on the track.
pushes on the front foot straight to the fielder at extra-cover.
looking to force it down the ground, mistimes to mid-on.
drifts down the leg side, nudged to fine leg, Taylor makes a mess of an easy fielding.
once again played down the fine leg, this time Taylor does well to field the ball and throw it in but the batsman is quick, completes the second run.
full delivery outside the off stump, gets the outside edge very fine to thirdman fence.
waits for the turn and cuts to the sweeper cover for a single.
cuts and misses outside the off stump as the ball spins away.
tossed up outside the leg stump, sweeps and gets a top-edge down to fine leg.
moves forward to the pitch of the delivery and drives along the ground straight to the fielder at extra-cover
cuts with the spin to backward point.
once again cut to the fielder at backward point.
fuller length delivery worked behind square leg to the deep.
digs in a short delivery outside the off stump, Chibhabha sways away from the line of the delivery.
goes for the big shot as the ball was pitched up outside the off stump, gets a thickish edge down to thirdman.
up on his toes and defends to the off side beside the track.
pitched up delivery wide outside the off stump, square drives it well to the right of thirdman.
works it nicely in front of square leg as the fielder comes in from the deep fields the ball.
moves back and pushes to extra-cover.
cut of the back foot to point.
down the track and plays it to the left of Lewis, who gets an hand to it.
defended to the off side.
down the track and plays to midwicket.
driven down the ground to long off.
digs in a short one and into the face, gets a glove to the on side and scampers through for a single, brings up his 50!. It is his 5th ODI fifty.
worked away on the on side for a single.
digs in a short one which goes a bit high and down the leg side, signaled a wide.
moves up and punches to mid-on. Powell cramping him.
defends on the front foot with an angled bat to point.
works it to the on side for a single.
yorker length delivery dug out to the off side.
a mistimed drive down to mid-off.
nice shot, sweeps it well in the air to midwicket fence.
tossed up on the off and middle, comes forward and pushes in the gap and scampers through for a quick single.
waits for the turn and cuts straight to the fielder at point.
moves back and pushes to the off side.
moves forward and plays to cover.
short ball pulled in the air behind square leg.
attempted yorker turns out into a low full toss, driven to mid-on.
driven on the up just wide of the fielder at short extra-cover to the deep.
digs in a short one which goes over the batsman, signaled wide.
slower delivery on the middle and leg, misses the bat, off the pad to square leg.
short delivery outside the off stump, Chibhabha goes for the pull and misses. Powell walks down the track and has few words with Chibhabha.
good reply from Chibhabha, drives in the air over extra-cover to the fence.

misses a run out chance, looks to work it to the on side, misses it, off the pad they scamper through for a single, Ramdin quickly onto it and throws it at the bowlers end, Lewis fails to gather it cleanly, misses a good chance.
defended on the back foot to the off side.
comes down the track and drives down the ground to long on.
short ball pulled to deep midwicket.
looking to sweep, misses it, off the pad behind the wicket
down the track to pitch of the delivery and drives well down the ground to long off, a slight misfield by Chanderpaul but recovers in time to keep it to one.
moves back and looks to work it to the on side, strikes the pad, appeal turned down, looks go down the leg side.
works it behind square leg.
moves forward and turns it behind square leg for another single.
moves back and pushes to cover.
moves forward and defends on the track.
works it in front of square leg, two fielders converge and mis-understanding among them, gives away an extra run.
played to the on side
sweeps and misses, off the pad.
moves forward and pushes to mid-off.
wonderful shot, down the track and picks it up nicely and launches it over wide long on for maximum, good strike from Chibhabha. This is now his highest score in ODI's
played to the off side for a single
works it off his legs to the on side.
moves forward and plays the reverse sweep to backward point.

Gayle picks up the wicket of Chibhabha, tosses it up outside the off stump and spins in, sweeps and misses, strikes the pad in line with the stumps, appeal upheld by the umpire. Chibhabha goes after a good knock.
defended to the off side
worked to the on side
moves back and turns it around behind square leg for a single.
waits for the turn and works to midwicket.
tossed up outside the leg stump, comes forward and defends to the off side.
down the track and turns it to square leg.
a beauty, turns across the batsman as it pitches on the leg stump, beats the outside edge.
defended on the front foot to the off side.
slips as he sweeps, but got good half of the bat down to fine leg.
pushes to the off side and takes off for a quick single, half way down the track and sent back as the throw from the cover fielder misses the stumps.
pushes to the off side for a comfortable single.
picks up his second wicket, tosses it up very full and Masakadza looks to work it through the on side, plays across the line and gets hit on the pad, loud appeal, given by the umpire.
played to the on side for a single.
worked to the on side.
moves forward and pushes backward of square on the off side, comes quickly for the second run, good running.
pushes forward and works through square leg.
spins away wide outside the off stump, cut to the sweeper cover, comes back for the second run, wonderful running.
pushes down the ground to deep mid-off, looking for the second run, the throw is in quickly prevents it.
on the middle and leg, comes forward and defends on the track.
wonderful delivery, lot of turn, pitches outside the leg stump and spins across, off the arm to the slip.
moves forward and pushes through cover.
driven square and behind the wicket on the off side to the deep, excellent running from both the batsmen.
moves forward and opens the face of the bat and runs it down to short thirdman, quick run taken.
this time played to the right of short thirdman.
plays to short cover and takes off for a quick run, Ramdin in quickly but fails to pick up the ball.
waits for the turn and works it behind square leg.
spins in from outside the off stump, looks to work it through the on side, misses it, off the pad the ball rolls along the track.
sweeps from off and middle to deep-backward square leg.
spins from outside the leg stump, pushes back to the bowler.
sweeps a full delivery tossed up outside the leg stump, off the pad to the off side.
moves back and plays to point.
moves forward and pushes to the left of point.
moves forward to the pitch of the delivery and drives well down the ground to long off.
plays to the off side
fullish delivery pushed to the off side.
great shot, Matsikenyari launches it over long on fence for maximum, lovely strike.
pushes to the off side.
played to deep mid-on for a single.
pushes forward and plays to the off side.
good ball, kicks up from a length, off the glove to the off side.
pitched up delivery driven down the ground to long on, wonderful running, comes back for the second run.
chips it over midwicket, great running once again.
slower delivery wide outside the off stump, signaled wide.
again a slower delivery wide outside the off stump, signaled a wide again, Taylor losing his line.
slower delivery, jumps up of a length, off the glove to the on side.
dabs it square of the wicket on the off side.
short delivery and into Matsikenyeri, jumps up and defends to the off side.
drops it beside the track on the off side and quick single taken.
fires it in, worked to the on side.
lovely strike, picks it up nicely and lofts it high and over midwicket fence, first boundary for Chigumbura.
moves forward and opens the face of the bat, plays to short thirdman.
driven to mid-on.
full and on the legs, off the pad to short fine leg.
full and drifting down the leg side, off the pad to the on side, they scamper through  for a leg-bye.
chops it to the left of backward point to the deep, thirdman runs around to field the ball.
short ball pulled well in front of square leg to the deep.
fuller delivery squeezed out to deep-backward square leg, fumble by Devon Smith, gives away the second run.
short ball pulled in the air behind square leg, Smith running sideways to his right fields it on the bounce.
slower delivery on the pads, worked to behind square leg.
full toss on the legs, clipped away to midwicket fence.
lovely shot, gave himself some room and strikes it firmly to the right of Gayle at extra-cover, who gets an hand to it.
good slower delivery outside the off stump, Matsikenyeri fails to pick it up, lets it go.
goes for the slog sweep on the slower delivery and gets a top-edge over the keeper, lands safely at fine leg.
mistimes the drive back to the bowler.
slower delivery, pushes to the off side.
short ball down the leg side, Matsikenyeri goes for the pull and gets a top-edge down to fine leg fence.
good shot, heaves it in the air to deep midwicket, of the ropes Samuels fields and pushes it in, umpire initially signaled it a 6 but then changed it to a four.
worked to midwicket
squeezes it down to fine leg.
walks down the track and hits it down the ground to long on, brings up the 250 for Zimbabwe.
swings it high in the air to deep-square leg, Smith fields it on the bounce.
fullish delivery worked to deep midwicket.
a thick inside edge to deep-backward square leg.
full and straight from Bravo, driven down the ground to long on.
amazing shot, gets it between his legs to long leg fence to bring up his 50! in style, 7th ODI fifty for him.
slower delivery, waits and then makes room and cuts to the sweeper cover.

slower delivery wide outside the off stump, was looking to heave it over the midwicket fence, too early into the shot and hits it in the air down to long on where Rampaul settles under it and takes the catch.
moves across and plays, misses it, off the pad and goes behind the wicket, stifled appeal from Taylor, turned down, they scamper through for a leg-bye.

full and straight, squeezed out behind square leg, comes back for the second run as Ramdin gets rid of the stumps, referred to the third umpire, given not out as the green light flashes, Matsikenyeri does well diving back into the crease.
played to midwicket
short ball pulled to deep midwicket.
makes room and looks to heave a full delivery to the midwicket fence, misses it completely and the leg stump is knocked back.
down the leg side
another full delivery on the stumps, goes for a big heave on the on side, misses it,  knocks the stumps back.
worked to square leg for couple of runs, good running.
short ball dug in, goes for the hook and misses, through to Ramdin.
slower delivery, plays and misses outside the off stump.
dropped! Slower delivery heaved away in the air to deep midwicket, Morton running in puts down a simple chance.
another slower delivery pitches it too short, comes down the track and misses, through to Ramdin.
another slower delivery outside the off stump to finish the over, Utseya has another heave and misses.

inn2.comm: short of a length delivery defended to the on side.
left alone outside the off stump.
short of a length delivery defended to the on side.
good ball angled across, left alone through to Taibu.
short of a length delivery angled across, lets it go outside the off stump.
fuller on the legs, pushes down the ground past mid-on to the deep, Gayle gets off the mark.
short delivery angled across, chops it down to backward point.
good ball short of a length and coming in, watches it well and lets it go trusting the bounce.
good ball swinging away, left alone through to Taibu
defended to the on side.
good ball back of a length, left alone through to Taibu.
good ball pitches on the stumps and moves away, moves in line and defends to the off side.
full and wide outside the off stump, lets it go.
moves back and pushes to the off side.

Gayle goes, Chigumbura strikes, pitches on a good length outside the leg stump, came slow off the track, Gayle too early into the shot, looking to work it to the on side, gets a leading edge back to Chigumbura.
left alone outside the off stump.
moves forward and lets it go outside the off stump.
left alone outside the off stump.
moves back to a short of a length delivery and works to the on side.
cut away nicely to cover fence. Smith gets the width he needed.
moves forward, covers the line and lets the ball go through to Taibu.
short and wide outside the off stump, cut hard to Taylor at cover.
worked behind square leg.
moves back and punches to cover.
short and wide outside the off stump, signaled wide.
beats the outside edge.
plays it back to the bowler.
driven on the up through the covers to the deep.
short and wide outside the off stump, cut to deep cover.
short ball pulled, gets an inside edge and goes to fine leg.
good length delivery pushed to the off side.
bang! hits it well down the ground to long on fence for maximum.
cuts and misses outside the off stump
defended to the off side.
moves in line and defends to the off side.
full on the legs, flicks it to deep square leg.
cuts in front of point
short ball, mistimes the pull shot to deep midwicket.
wide outside the off stump, Smith chases it and gets an edge through to Taibu behind the wicket.
full on the legs, clips it wide of mid-on to the deep.
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended to the off side.
drops it square of the wicket on the off side and takes off for a quick single, the fielder fails to pick up the ball cleanly, would have been a close thing.
loud appeal for lbw turned down. Pitches short of a length outside the off stump and strikes bit high on the pad.
left alone outside the off stump.
slower delivery, waits for it and nudges it to fine leg.
worked around his pads to long leg.
moves back and defends to the on side.
slower delivery pushed back to Brent.
fuller on the legs, worked to short fine leg.
moves across his stumps and lets the ball go outside the off stump.
short of a length delivery, works it behind square leg for a single.
moves back and pushes to cover.
off the pad to the on side
edge and dropped! Samuels slashes it hard on the front foot, gets the outside edge, the ball flies to the lone slip, who puts it down.
defended on the front foot to the on side
moves back and opens the face of the bat, steers it down to thirdman.
moves forward in line of the delivery and defends to point.
moves across his stumps and blocks it.
neatly tucks it behind square leg to the deep.
guides it down to thirdman, sloppy work from the fielders as the throw from thirdman is wide.
wide outside the off stump, Chanderpaul in a good position on the back foot cuts well to cover fence.
good ball short of a length slanting across Chanderpaul, cuts and misses.
again width but too early into the shot, chops it hard into the ground.
very wide from Chibhabha outside the off stump.
cuts down to thirdman for a single.
moves forward and pushes to backward point.
a leading edge down to thirdman.
good length delivery pushed to mid-on.
good length delivery on the stumps, moves across and defends to mid-on.
jumps up off the track as Samuels defends on the front foot, takes the glove and falls on the track.
moves forward and defends on the front foot to the off side.
good length delivery outside the off stump, watches it closely and lets it go through to Taibu.
slants it wide outside the off stump, left alone.
moves forward and drives through the off side to the sweeper cover.
short of a length outside the off stump, opens the face off the bat and runs it down to the left of backward point.
short ball pulled to Dabengwa at midwicket, lucky to get away with a short delivery.
moves forward and drives through the covers to the sweeper.
yorker length delivery dug out back to the bowler.
Chanderpaul breaks the shackles, picks it up nicely and swings it over the midwicket fence for maximum.
tucked away behind square leg to pick up a single.
pushed to the off side
slower delivery outside the off stump, left alone.
moves forward in line and defends well to the off side.
slower delivery outside the off stump, moves across his stumps and was looking to pull it over midwicket but then watches the length and pushes to the off side.
Chanderpaul plays across the line and lifts it in the air to deep midwicket.
mistimes the drive to cover.
low full toss driven to mid-on, fails to put it away.
classic shot from Samuels, a real juicy half-volley, puts his left forward and drives nicely through extra-cover to the fence.
waits on the back foot and glides it down to thirdman.
very wide outside the off stump, left alone.
fuller and wide outside the off stump, goes for the drive and gets the outside edge in the gap between the keeper and wide slip to thirdman fence.
worked to the on side.
moves forward and drives wide of mid-off.
fullish delivery driven to mid-off.
gets behind it and tucks it around the corner behind square leg.
forces off the back foot to cover.
lets the ball go outside the off stump, too wide to attempt any kind of shot.
chops it down to thirdman for a single.
full and drifting on the pads, fails to get contact, off the pad.
slower delivery too short outside the off stump, Samuels waits for it for ages and drives it in the gap between extra-cover and mid-off to the fence.
plays to the off side
driven to mid-off.
gets behind and works in front of square leg.
slashes it hard in the air to deep-backward point, thirdman runs around and does not field cleanly.
defended to the off side.
moves back in line and defends to the off side.
moves across his stumps and lets the ball go through to Ramdin. It was short in length outside the off stump.
moves across his stumps and defends it back to the bowler.
slower delivery, off the pad to the on side.
cut away to thirdman for a single.
moves back and cuts to backward point.
chops it down into the ground to the off side.
moves back and cuts down to thirdman, good fielding by Chigumbura at thirdman prevents the second run.
works it nicely to deep-backward square leg
